'''''A Google of [[Gornt/Legends|Gornts]]''''' was one of many [[Holodrama/Legends|holofilms]] denounced by the [[Core World Critics Association]] President [[Jaysa Namoor]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

==Behind the scenes==
The second word of the title seeming to call for a quantity, "Google" is perhaps an erroneous substitution for the homophone "[[Wikipedia:Googol|Googol]]," a number equal to 10<sup>100</sup>.

